data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful, light-filled, 3 bedroom 3.5 bath end unit townhome! This home has been beautifully renovated with all new LVP floors and carpet throughout which adds brightness to the main living level as you enter the home. The large bump-out window in the living room provides ample natural light. The spacious kitchen is fully-equipped with stainless steel appliances, plenty of countertop and cabinetry space (including a closet pantry) with back door leading to additional parking options. On the upper level of the home you will find the primary bedroom suite which features its own private en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms and a hall bath complete the level. The lower level of the home features brand-new floors and the third full bathroom as well as a bonus room (the perfect guest room!) and additional living space. This home is conveniently located within walking distance to the metro bus and 1.2 miles from Congress Heights Metro station, Anacostia, and Potomac Ave Metro/Subway Station. Walking distance to major Saint Elizabeth Development, Safeway, Banking and 1.1 miles to Eastern Market. Located off of Suitland Pkwy, I-295, I-495. National Harbor, National Stadium, Navy Yard, and Downtown DC. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this your own!
